data.description: Must Sale! Pre Foreclosure 4 beds 4 baths. No Banks or Credit needed! Buy this Home with $49,000 down and a $2500 monthly payment. Rate of 6.25% for those who qualify!  All newly renovated, new carpet, clean, and move-in ready! * Seller Financing Homes Available. Master Bedroom on the main level with private bathroom. NO HOA Community. Upstairs Bedrooms are spacious and there is a full bath. The carpet is newly installed Tile flooring on the main level. Fireplace in the family room with tons of space. The backyard is very peaceful. The location is great, just minutes to access the interstate and one exit away to shopping, restaurants, and businesses and a short 20-minute drive to Atlanta Airport.
